title: Custom Data Loader llamaindex
author: Pallavi Pannu
description:
Custom data loader where you can specify the number of documents to load from Cloud Object Storage and convert to llamaindex document objects.
It assumes that if you have a bucket in COS where you have say 1000 files, instead of loading all the files at once, it will load only the number of files that you specify.

installDependencyCommands: pip install tqdm, pip install nest_asyncio, pip install llama_index
